caption:
🌴✨ Hey WISA family! We're now broadcasting on WhatsApp Channels! 📢💬 

Stay in the loop with all the latest campus events, announcements, and more! 🎉 Don't miss out—join our channel now for the updates! 🤩

👉 Tap the link in our Linktree to join the WISA WhatsApp Channel and be part of the action! 🔗

#universityoftoronto #uoft #uoftwisa #uoftstudentlife #WhatsAppChannels #CampusLife #StayConnected #EventUpdates

WISA will also be attending the UTSU Clubs Fair! We’re so excited to be participating in the biggest clubs fair of the year! 🥳 

🗓️ Friday, August 30th, 2024
📍 Front Campus, St. George St. 
🕦 1pm - 4pm 

Come learn about WISA from our wonderful execs! Can’t wait to catch you there :) 

#uoft #wisa #universityoftoronto #uoftstudentlife

WISA will be tabling at the BIPOC Resource Fair! 🎡
Come chat with us, learn about what we do, and take some goodies back with you! 

🗓️ Thursday, August 29th, 2024
📍 20 Willcocks Ave. 
🕦 3pm-5pm 

Our mission is to foster a vibrant community for Caribbean students on campus, offering support, connection, and a sense of belonging. Join us as we celebrate our diverse heritage and work together to create a more inclusive environment for all! 🥳 

See you there! 🤞🏽

#uoftwisa #uoft #universityoftoronto #westindian #uoftstudentlife
